{"tid":188851,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[樓爆]其實係咪2047地契問題未搞清楚，都唔好買樓住？","createTime":"2017-04-06T04:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T09:29:41.000Z","uid":103921,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26e98aa31c4af081e47608b4ff5c291af271a8e9","tid":188851,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"如果香港冇一個續租土地使用權既機制<br />\n買樓就好大風險，97果陣免費續左去2047<br />\n但係宜家支那同香港關係緊張<br />\n好大機支那會會鏈住港豬春袋，唔續住<br />\n或者玩到2047叫你比個勁貴既租去續，即係繼續供<br />\n支那之前唔少呢d例子<br />\n就算買新樓，減返起樓果幾年，都係得四十幾年使用權<br />\n宜家個個對呢樣野避而不談，有伏味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72eae7d3c336f50e0a0eaab702ba4ca7a7467b94","tid":188851,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:08:39.000Z","msg":"講左好耐<br />\n2047之後無特別行政區<br />\n直接強拆都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a5ac57bf9b85ad2edf4e75b2792074ba6d6db1","tid":188851,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:10:05.000Z","msg":"30年後自己仲係唔係呢個世界都唔知啦,邊擔心得咁多"},{"pid":"b0d549033b307ae5d3fced2b30593dca8277b6ed","tid":188851,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/180368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/180368/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"58aba4866ecb2c9180316f3f90ec68ff74024520","tid":188851,"uid":30478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"強拆就乜都冇晒<br />\n<br />\n但係租樓你從頭到尾都係1蚊都冇<br />\n除非你住屋企，可以唔租樓幾十年"},{"pid":"3ec6117101f3e1db469d9e2f24251aae8423ed9b","tid":188851,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"不停話買樓冇得輸<br />\n其實有樓都係想供斷<br />\n但係其實背後仲有好多支出<br />\n地稅,差餉就梗左架喇<br />\n<br />\n管理費呢?私樓有會所貴就梗架喇<br />\n<br />